OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,FDozens of prominent individuals and
OL,7,Forganisations from across civic
OL,8,Fsociety have signed a letter
OL,9,Fcriticising Stormont's plan to target
OL,10,Fpoverty.
OL,12,FThe signatories said they are
OL,13,F"dismayed and frustrated" at the
OL,14,FExecutive's Anti-Poverty Strategy 2025-
OL,15,F35.
OL,17,FThe letter has been signed by
OL,18,Forganisations, charities, community
OL,19,Fgroups, campaigners, unions, academics
OL,20,Fand religious representatives.
