OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,FThe open letter, published on Monday,
OL,7,Fsaid the strategy does not meet the
OL,8,Fcriteria of a "reasonable strategy".
OL,10,F"It fails to fulfil what oversight
OL,11,Fbodies, including the NI Audit Office
OL,12,Fand Public Accounts Committee, outline
OL,13,Fas the basic elements of any
OL,14,Fstrategy," it added.
