OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,F"The NI Audit Office said that 'an
OL,7,Fintegrated cross-departmental anti-
OL,8,Fpoverty strategy (should) ensure that
OL,9,Fthe focus is on a number of properly
OL,10,Fdefined and more specific actions" and
OL,11,F"it should include an action plan
OL,12,Fcontaining clearly defined indicators
OL,13,Fand targets aimed at quantifying and
OL,14,Freducing poverty'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]sD@AOU
