OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,F"The Public Accounts Committee said
OL,7,Fthat there is a 'clear need for
OL,8,Ftargets and outcomes that are
OL,9,Fquantitative, qualitative and time-
OL,10,Fbound to properly measure performance
OL,11,Fand demonstrate the impact of
OL,12,Fstrategic actions'.
OL,14,F"It also considered that 'a strategy
OL,15,Fwhich does not have specific resources
OL,16,Fdevoted to it is never going to be as
OL,17,Feffective as it could be'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
