OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,F"We acknowledge that the (Communities)
OL,7,FMinister (Gordon Lyons) has indicated
OL,8,Fthat an action plan with targets and
OL,9,Fspecific actions will follow at a
OL,10,Flater, unspecified date, but every
OL,11,Fexpert, every oversight body, is clear
OL,12,Fthat a strategy must include
OL,13,Fmeasurable and time-bound targets
OL,14,Fwithin or alongside the strategy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@bO]
