OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,FThey urged the minister to note
OL,7,Fresearch published by the Independent
OL,8,FExpert Advisory Panel (2020), the Anti-
OL,9,FPoverty Strategy Co-Design Group
OL,10,F(2022), the Welfare Reform Mitigation
OL,11,FReview (2021) and the Discretionary
OL,12,FSupport Review (2022).
OL,14,FThey said the research provides clear
OL,15,Fevidence of the interventions that
OL,16,Fwork to tackle poverty.
