OL,3,CCharities 'dismayed and frustrated' at
OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,FThe letter added: "We are committed to
OL,7,Fworking with you in good faith to
OL,8,Feradicate poverty in Northern Ireland,
OL,9,Fand therefore, we are asking the NI
OL,10,FExecutive to withdraw their support of
OL,11,Fthe draft anti-poverty strategy, on
OL,12,Fthe basis that it is more harmful to
OL,13,Fhave a strategy that will not address
OL,14,Fpoverty than no strategy at all.
OL,16,F"Our children, families and
OL,17,Fcommunities ` your constituents `
OL,18,Fdeserve better."
