OL,4,CStormont's Anti-Poverty Strategy
OL,6,FThe strategic commitments from across
OL,7,Fdepartments include continuing the
OL,8,FExtended Schools Programme, working
OL,9,Fwith partners to scope out an NI Debt
OL,10,FRelief Scheme, a commitment to develop
OL,11,Fan Executive Disability Strategy and a
OL,12,FFuel Poverty Strategy.
OL,14,FSpeaking in the Assembly, Mr Lyons
OL,15,Fdescribed a "legacy of delay" in
OL,16,Ftaking forward an anti-poverty
OL,17,Fstrategy.
